name: Gatot Kaca Panda - KuD-048
description: In pandas universe, there are a lot of folklore and myth like ours have. There exist Mahabharatha story too, and this is one of important character in the story as the son of bima. Like how the story told, he have muscles made of wire and bone made of steel. He have incredible power unlike his peers and he is a brave warior which always win in battlefield.
